      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "有一个数字，藏着让人吃惊的魔力，它叫 6174。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kaprekar",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kaprekar/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "随便挑一个四位数，只要数字不全相同，就能玩一个小游戏。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kaprekar",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kaprekar/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "反复做同一件事，最后你几乎总会掉进 6174 这个坑里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kaprekar",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-1",
      "filename": "rule-rule-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kaprekar/xiaoxiao/rule-rule-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "把四位数的各个数字，从大到小排出一个最大数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kaprekar",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-2",
      "filename": "rule-rule-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kaprekar/xiaoxiao/rule-rule-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.18,
      "size": 18864,
      "text": "再从小到大排出一个最小数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kaprekar",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-3",
      "filename": "rule-rule-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kaprekar/xiaoxiao/rule-rule-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "用最大数减去最小数，就得到下一个四位数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kaprekar",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "conv-1",
      "filename": "converge-conv-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kaprekar/xiaoxiao/converge-conv-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "拿这个结果再做一次重排相减，然后一次又一次。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kaprekar",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "conv-2",
      "filename": "converge-conv-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kaprekar/xiaoxiao/converge-conv-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.74,
      "size": 43776,
      "text": "神奇的是，从 1000 到 9999，几乎每个数都会走到 6174。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kaprekar",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "conv-3",
      "filename": "converge-conv-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kaprekar/xiaoxiao/converge-conv-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22320,
      "text": "而且最多只要七步，绝不会更多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kaprekar",
      "section_id": "constant",
      "line_id": "const-1",
